      "title": "The number of people infected with Covid is increasing",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The number of Covid infected people reported from Sri Lanka seems to be growing rapidly. Thus, the number of infected people identified today has increased to 62.",
        "With this number of infected people, the number of Covid infected people reported from Sri Lanka has grown to 664510. However, no covid deaths were reported yesterday."
